<h2><span class="badge bg-warning"><i class="fab fa-leanpub"></i> Yeshua in the Tanakh</span></h2>

<p class="text-muted"><small><i>Tanakh</i> is the Old Testament</small></p>

<p class="h5">
	<b>Luke 24:13-34</b> tells the story of two disciples who were walking on the road to Emmaus, talking with each other about the recent death of Yeshua.
	They were joined on their journey by the resurrected Messiah.
</p>

